# CODEOWNERS — every change to a security-sensitive path requires review
# from the repository owner before merging.
#
# GitHub enforces this automatically when branch protection rules require
# CODEOWNER approval. Enable "Require review from Code Owners" in:
#   Settings → Branches → Branch protection rules for "main"

