# CODEOWNERS itself — prevent self-approval of ownership changes.
/.github/CODEOWNERS     @socialstrategyapp-boss

# Security policy and documentation.
/SECURITY.md            @socialstrategyapp-boss
/docs/                  @socialstrategyapp-boss

# Repository root — catch anything not covered above.
